snippet.title: Projekt Z: Beyond Order - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Projekt Z: Beyond Order is an atmospheric First-Person Zombie Co-Op-Shooter set in WW2. Play as a diverse crew of survivors, each with their own unique abilities, to unravel the secrets of the Nazi-controlled island. You can wishlist Projekt Z: Beyond Order on Steam now. Coming soon to PC, Xbox Series X|S, and PlayStation 5.
